"Don't forget to enable payment provider, in the video we used the \"demo\" "
"provider that accepts any data.<br/>\n"
"                    You can do that in Sales -&gt; Configuration -&gt; "
"Payment Provider.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Husk at aktivere betalingsudbyderen. I videoen har vi brugt “Demo”, som "
"accepterer alle data.<br/>\n"
"                    Det kan gøres under Salg -&gt; Konfiguration -&gt; "
"Betalingsudbydere.<br/>"

